Description: Provides a unified interface for estimating, benchmarking, and visualizing
    predictive uncertainty across classical statistical and machine learning models.
    Supports bootstrap, jackknife, Bayesian sampling, and conformal prediction intervals,
    including diagnostic plots and benchmarking utilities.
